<li><strong>00.31:55</strong> &#8211; Lesenswertes <a href="http://www.squidinabox.com/2012/04/waves-the-postmorteming/" target="_blank">Postmortem</a> des Waves-Entwicklers (s. <a href="http://www.wirschweifenab.de/wp/?p=181" target="_blank">WSA #6</a>)</li>
